query:
SELECT id
        FROM data.entities_place
        WHERE data.ST_DWithin(
            geo_center::data.geography,
            data.ST_SetSRID(data.ST_MakePoint($1, $2), 4326)::data.geography,
            $3
        )
        ORDER BY data.ST_Distance(
            geo_center::data.geography,
            data.ST_SetSRID(data.ST_MakePoint($1, $2), 4326)::data.geography
        )
        LIMIT 1
